data.description: In the heart of Euless, this single story home offers 4 bedrooms, 1 full bath & 2 half baths, plus a 2 car garage in an established neighborhood. The spacious kitchen features an island, breakfast bar & abundant cabinet space & opens to the dining room with vaulted ceilings & wood beam. The nook off the kitchen provides great extra storage space. Step down living room with French doors. Split bedroom layout & flexible floorplan. Great-sized backyard with covered patio & storage shed! New roof in Jan 2023 with 5 yr transferable warranty & new attic insulation in 2021. Great opportunity to be minutes from DFW Airport, central to Dallas & Fort Worth & close to 183, 360 & 121.
